To say DragonCultistsdesc:
	if Morale of Arlene < 10:
		say "     Milling about their chambers between work shifts, this small, tightly knit group of caucasian women were the first to Tiamat's and your children's call. Utterly loyal and profoundly driven, most found their way to Pirate Island on their own power, or at least tried before being rescued by your spawn after hearing your flight's call. To that end, they are willing to bear any hardship in the hopes that they may earn the salvation promised to them. Hardened by their labor and rigors of the apocalypse, your trim, athletic followers have eschewed the use of clothing at the urging for your priestess and simple necessity as few garments can survive the attentions of your spawn. Observing some walk past you on their way to their chambers, you can't help but admire their proud sensual stride and the playful pop of their tight perky asses as they go by. The sight of their shapely hips and thighs too, toned and molded by the harshness of the world into lithe limbs befitting a professional runner or swimmer, rarely fails to bring a devilish smirk to your lips. Perhaps feeling your eyes upon them, the little morsel flashes you a knowing sideways glance as she pops mid step and nods to her chambers.";
		if Libido of Dragon Cultist is 0: [not knocked up]
			say "     Smirking at the brash human's forwardness, you can't help but notice the lovely blush of her cunt, or the gentle bounce of her supple C-cups as the brave and comely women beckons you to join her with a come hither wave of arms.";
		else if Libido of Dragon Cultist >= 1:
			say "     As she turns to face you though, you can't be chuff approvingly at the site of the sensual swell of her tender blushing eggy tum, which is no doubt a result of her prior coupling with you or one of your spawn. Feeling the weight of your molten gaze upon her, the little human playfully arches her back to better highlight her wondrous condition while her left hand drifts to the verdant swell of her delectable D-cups as she coyly traces her nails along the perky swell of her milky breasts. As beads of pure alabaster delight drip from her perky rosy nips, then down along the silky curves of her ripening middle and pool along the blushing hem of the shameless human's eggy bump. Her comely face is soon set alight with unbound glee at the gentle patter of her cream resounding throughout the halls as the shimmering droplets of milk and what you suspect is gossamer fem honey drips on the floor as she beckons you to follow her.";
	[else if Morale of Arlene >= 11 and Morale of Arlene < 20:
		if Loyalty of Dragon Cultist is 1:
			say "     Strutting through the now properly lit hall, the sight of your growing flock of humans walking along with their pets is odd, but welcome one as though the two groups may once not have been on the best of terms. Their devotion to you and one another has quickly eroded any misgiving your cults might have upon their first arrival, besides as many have noted, it's hard to stay mad at the adorable slut puppies for long. As just a simple glance from the sweet little subby bitches cute happy faces, or lovely hug from the one of the goofy fluffy balls is enough to put a smile on even the jaded of your lithe and hale cultist's faces. Though some seem to enjoy the feeling of superiority they get from ordering around their former captors and occasional tormentors pets. Thankfully, the huskies seem content to simply serve as the have heads command, while a few have even earned of horror of becoming bed warmers for your followers during the colder evenings.";
		if Libido of Dragon Cultist >= 1:
			say "    Although many of the budding broodmares among your followers number have taken a special shine to their new pets, as the wondrous cocktail of maternal nanite laced hormones has made them more than a little amenable to subby canine affections. Thankfully, there have been no reports of any transformations from their resulting liaison, and the more experimental among your cult even claim their pet oral affection have become a balm for the burning need imposed upon them by their draconic young. Others though, have come to openly crave their touch as they revel in the high of pregnancy enhanced orgasms or wallow in the loving embrace of their pets they pamper their growing curves. While a few prudes still resist their body's growing urges and even go so far as to push aside the odd overeager bitch when they get too close. Even now you can see a number for you follower's eye longing explore the curves of their peers flush tums and perky milk tanks as their through the halls with their doe eyed pets in tow.";
	else if Loyalty of Dragon Cultist is 2:
		say "     Inspired by your example and the urgings of your priestess, many of you cultists are slowly blossoming into an adorable mix of domineering breeders obsessed over the blissful changes brought on by their pregnancies, and demure subby helpers who dote upon their growing curves. Though a part of you considers putting a stop to this, the sight of some of your brash and indolent broodmares as they lounge on their furry blankets as they fawning over their taut ripe curves of their well-egged tums while whispering encouragement to their broods stills such thought. As despite their growing lackadaisical attitudes of your breeders towards work, your budding broodmothers commitment to growing your flight's numbers is an important task in and of itself. You muse, watching as others argue over whose litter will be the largest or strongest, or proudly preening to their apprentices over the expansive swell of their milky tits as their nimble minder massages and encourages their growth. "; 
		say "     As already many of your more dominant broodmothers have begin sporting delectable D-cups and wide birthing hips. Not that you can't say you aren't enjoying their antics either, as few could blame the lowly humans for wishing to coddle your draconic spawn as your eggs deserve a soft, quiet place for them to grow free of stress or worry. Besides, some of their number have taken to serving as midwives or instructs for you neophytes as they teach them how best to serve their draconic masters. While others have become consummate mates of your deep dwelling spawn, your remaining flock is more than enough to continue the great work going on around the temple, and serve as potent reminder that should your lovely breeder ever fail to entice your spawn. They will soon toil alongside their lessers until they can regain the favor of your spawn, either way they all still serve as the five heads commands.";
	else if Loyalty of Dragon Cultist is 3:
		say "     Enthused by their changes, your cultist rarely passes up a chance to proudly flaunt their scales and draconic eyes to you and their peers, or to beg for the opportunity to share a moment's passion with your or your young in the hopes your flight's aberrant nanites will rub off on them. Of course, you and brood need little encouragement as the sight of the happy breeder glowing bumps, flush milky D-cups and glittering lamina is becoming a common feature among your cultists. Even now, the halls gleam with the vibrant shimmer of the blue scales or the gold draconic reflecting in the available light. While the area resounds with the pleasant chatter and the occasionally aphonic creak of their perky milk tank accompanied by the gentle patter of the thin beads of pearly cream leaking down the lush swell of taut tums, or the well-pleased coos of the mothers-to-be as their once lithe hips continue to blossom into wide curvy flanks befitting of a proper Dragon Breeders."; 
		say "     Overjoyed by the changes, their devotion to the cause deepens with each litter, and many have taken to praying to their lush tums in the hope that their slumbering young will bless with further changes. Though many of them sadly appear to be afflicted with modest resistance to the glory of draconic ascension, this hasn't stopped them from trying to entice the notice of their draconic masters. Nor has it impeded them from entreating the aid of their more advanced peers in the fervent hope they may begin to take the first steps on the path of ascension. A fact some of amongst their number are happy to exploit, as a few of your more brazen supplicants have adopted these poor unfortunate to into their [']care['] as they instruct them in the proper methods of dragon worship. That such [']worship['] off take the of foot rub or the odd hand feeding session is not lost on you, yet you are of no mind to stop them so long as work on the temple remains uninterrupted, and your flights numbers continue to expand.";
	else if Morale of Arlene >= 21 and Morale of Arlene < 30:
		if Loyalty of Dragon Cultist is 1:
			say "     As their ranks swell, the growing pair bond between your lovely human followers and the cuddly bitches has only deepened in the days since the first group of pups was brought to the temple grounds. Though some might have once quietly balked at the idea of living together with the fluffy quasi-ferals, the two are becoming inseparable, but not without consequence. As you've noticed a growing softness in your once hale and lithe followers physique as their husky pets have slowly begun assisting them in their day-to-day lives. Though not a wholly unwelcome occurrence as their comforting presences, not to mention their constant heats has helped to slowly erode your cultist's lingering inhibitions as ever more of their number have to embrace their ultimate roles as the mothers of your wondrous flight. Even now, the halls are a buzz with happy chatter of your happy broodmares as they gush of the sensual swell of their well-egged tums, or sing the praise of doting slut puppies care.";
			say "    Many openly delight at the unbound bliss of their nanite touched pregnancy impart upon as they pamper their tender tums and ripe D-cups as if to encourage their growth. Their pets too seem equally enamored by the spreading softness coddling the mistresses' widening hips and shapely thighs as their slumber brood slowly mold their mothers into the perfect vessels. All to the huskies delight as the libidinous changes have served to erode what's left of your cultists inhibitions as they now joyfully welcome their pet's advances.";
	else if Loyalty of Dragon Cultist is 2:
		say "     As the cult's commitment to the exaltation of hedonism and dominance deepens, so to does the waistlines of your most eager of breeders, as time spent lounging about their chamber or beneath your virile progeny has worn away much of their former athletic physique. Coddled a thin pleasing layer of supple motherly adipose, your voluptuous broodmares joyously wile away their day under the constant care of their lessers with little concerns of anything other than the well-being of their eggs, and attending the needs of your many progeny. As their formerly trim bodies now sport a supple set of plush yet profoundly perky E-cups, while the barest hints of supple love handles creep along the edges of their well-egged tums. Their arms and legs too have lost most of their definition behind silky swaddling of shapely jiggly pudge befitting their status as prolific breeders.";
		say "    Meanwhile, your braver dragon mothers seem to have followed a slight different path as their own busts have grown slightly larger as host a perpetually set milks of silky DD's. Otherwise, their bodies remain as trim and lithe as ever as their time spent serving your flight and cultivating their coterie of mates leaves them with little time for self indulgence. As for the dwindling number of midwives and ubiquitous lesser humans, they appear more or less unchanged by the rising tide of gluttony and slothfulness sweeping through their ranks. Though some show glimmers of gravid potential, as some happily parade their latest hard earned clutch about the hall or cast a longing glance in your direction as you walk by. They remain beneath your notice, for at least.";
	else if Loyalty of Dragon Cultist is 3:
		say "     Little by little, your cults are leaving behind more of their worthless humanity for all their time spent in close proximity to one another, and the constant affections of you and your wondrous spawn have begun to bear the most wondrous of fruits. As many of your followers can now proudly call themselves half-dragon as a great deal of your senior followers now gleefully boast their own set of cute swept back ivory horns or adorable tiny spaded tails reminiscent of the old one gifted to you by Tiamat not so long ago. With this though, has come a noticeable shift in the demeanor of your more blessed servant as their profound pride in their accomplishment has only served to deepen their changing bodies desire for worship. As most of your ascending flock have begun coaxing the unenlightened into their service with the vain promise that though subservience to them and their ofttimes brood-laden bodies, they too may at last free themselves from their lowly humanoid form.";
		say "    While you can't say for certain if there is any truth to their words, their chosen methods nevertheless aid the cult in its ultimate goal of growing as the lewd demi-dergs are routine entourage their lesser to offer their bodies to you and your spawn so that their eggs may yet wear away at their resistance. Nor can you deny that you don't take a certain bit of pleasure at the sight of your gravid mostly human supplicants fawning over their better as lovingly pamper the growing curves of the budding half-dragons. Under their care and the loving attention of your spawn, the former warmbloods are steadily blossoming into buxom broodmares as the once cute C-cups have rounded out into tight, perky DD's capped with plush pluff nips. Their hips are have flared out, gifting with their tight toned asses with a neigh on hypnotic swagger the little dragons-to-be revel in.";
	else if Morale of Arlene >= 31 and Morale of Arlene < 40:
		if Loyalty of Dragon Cultist is 1:
			say "     Buoyed by the affections of their loyal husky pets and heady scent of their constant canine heat, your cultist have taken yet another welcome step down the path of brood motherdom as evermore of your followers have come to not only embrace the joys of dragon breeding, but actively crave the euphoric rush their nanite tainted pregnancies brings them. Most, if not all of your cultists have at least two or three clutches under their belt, and show little so slowing down as a playful competitive air is slowly sweeping the ranks. Your cultists now openly boast of the changes to their bust, and more than once measuring tapes have been brought to disputes over who is the milksiest of them all. While others jokingly argue who will have whelped the most young by the time of your ascension, or teasingly pontificate about who has the largest litter. But this change has not come without consequence as your followers are spending more fawning over their eggs then working, and most have started to lose their former harden physique beneath a tasteful layer of shapely motherly curves.";
			say "    All to their delight though, for your sensual breeders welcome these changes with open arms and spread legs as they view them as gifts from the goddess. Their jubilant attitude towards these changes almost seems to be infectious as their husky pets try to help their mistresses in their way by caringly suckling and stimulating their owner's productive glands, ensuring they run dry. Under their expert care, your cults bust have grown considerably over time and most happily flaunt flush DD's or perky E-cup even if they are not expecting. Yet others have come to play matchmaker for their owners as prowl the halls and do their best to attract the attention of your spawn to ensure their beloved masters are rarely without child. To their credit, your descendants have taken this rather well and even seem to enjoy the Husky's antics.";
	else if Loyalty of Dragon Cultist is 2:
		say "     Flushed with the raw bounty of the deep, your dominant and decadent breeder's waistlines continue to expand as their increasingly indolent lifestyle alongside the doting care of their lesser peers steadily wears away at their once trim figures. As their plush doughy tums have ripen into cute not-so-little muffin tops swaddled in a sensuous layer of silky pudge, perfect for keeping your flight eggs safe, as they steady round out into tight glisten spheres of fertile excess. Many of them though are bejeweled in thin rosy stretch marks radiating out from the deepening navel, far from ashamed by their growing tiger stripes, your overly fertile cults appear to be utterly enamored with their fecund figures and blissful changes wracking their bodies. Fed by their lavish lifestyle and the needs of their prodigious broods, their tits have swollen to all the decedent proportions as they lush milky F-cups lovingly laze atop their glowing bumps and bump-to-be.  Rivulets of warm gently bead form their puffy perky nips in endless stream of pearlescent perfection, regardless of their condition, all to the delight of your flight and your lesser cultists.";
		say "     Their limbs meanwhile, continue to soften to with litter as subtle rows of maternal tallow gracefully coddle their arms and legs, by no means off putting their pleasant girth only to their demeanor. So to do their plush heart-shaped asses and deep jiggling love handles add to their lovely voluptuous figures. A feature your lesser followers seem to take great pride as many of your less fertile cultists open gush of their mistress voluptuous bodies they attend to them. Though some still scoff at them, decrying the notion that only few should be so blessed, and the lack of care given to newer members. Their voices are dwindling by the day as more of the altruistic members and midwives remaining within your cult are slowly surrendering to their more dominant peer's will. In the background, your more clever cultist and their growing coterie of mates are slowly gaining power and size as few dare stand up to them or their lovers. Gifted with many litter all their own, they curvaceous bodies now boast tasteful D-cups and wide stocky hips well suited for breeders of their status.";
	else if Loyalty of Dragon Cultist is 3:
		say "     Overjoyed by their changes, your naturally ascending cultists have begun to reach new heights of morphic bliss as their lower bodies are at long last taking on the beastly appearance of a proper dragon. As more than a few of your senior cultists now proudly sport a toned set blue digitigrade legs coated in beautiful scales with a splotch of creamy white scales running along their inner thighs and plush scalie cunts. Their feet have been replaced by powerful draconic paws graced silky pink pads and tipped with scything ivory talons. Meanwhile, their height too has noticeably increased as the budding half-dragons now easily tower a few heads above their peers, much to their delight. As the proud dragons-to-be seem to revel in not only their stature, but the regal strength of their toned amazonian legs which have made the once difficult task of carrying their many draconic eggs a trivial affair. The fact their roiling heats have made this a more common occurrence is not lost on them, not that any among them are complaining as the coiling scent of their draconic lust serves a potent lure for your spawn.";
		say "   Nor would they have it any other way, as their pregnancies seem to accelerate their changes in more ways than one. For your more enlightened followers now boast an impressive set of perky E-cups, perfect for feeding their little one, or serving as lovely pillows for doting hoards of admirers. Ever eager to bask in their senior's draconic splendor in the hopes they too might join their beatific ranks, the more human among them continue to idolize their more evolved fellows. Which the budding half-dragons happily exploit as graciously allow their [']apprentices['] to spoil and coddle them and their broods. Even now as you walk the halls, you can spy whole teams of doe-eyes novices fawn over one such lucky half-dragoness as they playfully massage their spawn laden tums, or blissfully suckle from the ripening tits. Though as you watch them services their betters, you can can't help notice patches fresh scales form along their athletic curves.";
	else if Morale of Arlene >= 41 and Morale of Arlene < 50:
		if Loyalty of Dragon Cultist is 1:
			say "     Lavished by the constant care of the impressive husky pack, alongside the swelling comforts of the cult, your pampered broodmares have begun to truly embrace their roles as the mothers of your flight and seem all the happier for it. As the jolly competitive air bubbling through the halls has lead your followers and pets bonding their shared love of breeding and gravity in a way the more senior among might not have thought possible not all that long ago. Now everywhere you look, your cultists are aglow with maternal splendor and motherly bounty as their lovely conditions continue to mold their fecund bodies into the perfect vessels for your brood. As the vivacious breeders proudly flaunt their curvaceous body to one another, the hall resounds with their good natured chatters as they brag about the size of the current litters, and growing contributions to the goddess's coming. These are not idle boasts either, as their nanite enhanced bodies continue to ripen by the day, as of your formerly lithe followers bodies are blessed with an increasingly curvy build.";
			say "     By no means fat, or out of shape, the tasteful flaring of their hips and supple padding on their thighs is a rather flattering and altogether fitting addition to your breeder's motherly physique. One that is further enhanced by their radiant bumps, as any reluctance even the coldest of fish among their number has been washed by their time spent amongst your virile spawn and the constant exposure to their pet's heady heats. Not that any seem to mind as their borderline obsession over their changing body only deepens their love of their sumptuous curves and flush milky E-cups breasts. A feeling that's shared by not only their husky pets as the doting canines have developed quite the appetite for their mistresses cream over the course of their stay, but your spawn as well. For their part, your caring draconic spawn have come to favor the lush offerings of their worshipers almost as much as they do the rich fare regaling the halls.";
		else if Loyalty of Dragon Cultist is 2:
			say "      As if in emulation of your debauched tastes, the [']cows['] as the deep dwelling humans and their draconic mates have started to call your Rubenesque breeders continue to descend into gluttonous hedonism as these sedentary sows have almost completed surrendered to their basest needs. Utterly unconcerned with anything other their bodies and broods needs, these ravenous broodmares bear little resemblance to the harden lithe survivors you once knew, as their lean, trim muscular legs have given way to soft doughy thighs and curvaceous calves. While deep pillowy love handles deep enough to swallow a wolftaur's paw in their silky fold grace their fertile flanks and wide shelf like asses. Their titanic tums have rounded out into truly ostentatious tallow laden excess that dominate much of their view and constantly force their legs apart with the sheer weight of their turgid middles. Meanwhile their colossal milk perched atop their the heavenly mounds of their fertile midriff have blossomed into heaving H-cups, that groan and slosh enticingly with their breath as their wondrously flushed glands struggle to contain their motherly bounty.";
			say "    Their arms too are swaddled in plush pillowy padding and are ill suited for manual labor, but perfect for snuggling their many young as they drink in their first meal. In stark contrast, their many feeders and the odd midwife remain as hale as ever, and in some cases some have even gained a subtle six pack as the day of intense labor and hearty meals has continued to tone their bodies. Through a few of them are sporting tiny blushing bumps of their own, and openly eye their feedee's curves with an envious twinkle in their eyes. Overseeing them all though are the deep dwelling humans and the coterie of draconic lovers, kept fit by the constant attention of your spawn. These buxom amazonian breeders stride with a pronounced predatory grace that commands the respect of the largest cow while their plush D-cups and drum taut tum bounce hypnotically with their every step.";
	else if Loyalty of Dragon Cultist is 3:
		say "     As the cult's numbers continue down the path of ascension, the once domineering attitude toward their less evolved peers adopted by your more advanced flock has slowly melted away in the face of their shared love of their draconic splendor, gravidity, and commitment to hastening in the goddesses arrival. Working together to hasten their own transformation, and aided by the affections of your spawn, a number of your elated cults have begun to sprout tiny wings of their own alongside a smattering of opalescent scales flowing down their arms. Nowhere near flight capable, these latest adorable additions continue to encourage your cultist though none appear able to fully transform with your assistance. Still, the sight of your dragons-to-be fluttering their new wings only encourages your followers to continue down the path of draconic motherhood.";
		say "     Not that they needed the urging, as the motherly dragon girls fecund example and the coiling scent of draconic heat filling the halls never ceases to inspire them. Or you, as the lovely spectacle of your many demi-dreg followers proudly basking in their tall yet supple motherly figures as they strut about their chambers, never fails to bring a smile to your muzzle or your followers. As their plush blushing bumps and taut F-cup milk tanks radiant a bountiful glow that seems to almost illuminate the space around them. While scale shine all the brighter in the ";
		if "Touched by Madness" is listed in feats of Player:
			say "torches ";
		else:
			say "lanterns ";
		say "light, prompting many of your loyalists to openly gush over the prismatic hues refraction off them. Of course such displays pale your own splendor, yet you are not so proud, or jaded that you can't enjoy their hard earn changes, for soon all these lovely creatures will earn the right to join your flight."; 
	else if Morale of Arlene >= 51:
		if Loyalty of Dragon Cultist is 1:
			say "     Almost totally unencumbered by wants or needs, your pampered cults and their loyal pack of Husky Bitches now live a life of luxury few, if any survivors could dream of. Your followers can, at long last, finally kick back and enjoy the hard-earned comforts of the Temple with their pets. As their doting Bitches have taken over almost all their mistress's duties, allowing your jovial cults to totally devote themselves to their informal breeding competition. Though by no means mean-spirited, your follower's growing obsession over their burgeoning bodies has brought them closer than ever as they happily gush over the achievement of their fellows, or showering encouragement upon their newer members. Much to the delight of both your flight and their pets, as none can resist their growing curves and bubbly maternal charms as your lovely breeders have fully blossomed into living fertility idols that would put many ferals to same.";
			say "    Your senior broodmares tits have ripened to lush breasts perky F-cups, much the envy of the junior cults as open eye their peer silky sloshing milk tanks with avaricious delight. As few can resist the hypnotic wobble of their heavenly sweater puppies accompanying their motion, or the unending allure of the thick beads of pearly cream trickling from their puffy nips. Alongside the spreading softness swaddling their bodies in velvety blanket of motherly padding, utterly inviting to the touch, their silky muffin tops provide the perfect for your talons, and an adorable cushion for your flight's eggs. While their legs and hips are all the curvier still, though you would hesitate to call them fat, as a hidden core of dense muscle provides their shapely lower half with a certain classical grace befitting of a venus figurine that rarely fails to inspire your junior. Even eager to assist the novices growth, your more experienced cults, not to mention the huskies take great pride in mentoring them in the proper methods of dragon worships and instilled in the importance of heralding your ascension.";
		else if Loyalty of Dragon Cultist is 2:
			say "     Little more than demanding ravenous wombs, the cultist's [']cows['] have fully embraced their place as incubators for your spawn, plaything for your brood's boundless lust, or delectable meals for your own deviant appetites. Not that any among the cult can complain as the Rubenesque figure of the cult's cows have a point of pride for the lesser members, for the various harems now tirelessly work to feed and pamper their mistress's figures in an endless attempt to outdo another. Under this lavish condition, your lustrous fodder's oceanic bodies are swaddled in a dense yet profoundly soft tallow, betting their status as the cult's baby factories. Laden with comely adipose, your broodmares are easily dwarfed by their supple perpetually round tummies, coated in a vibrant spider web of thicc ruby stretch marks arrayed around their plush outies. While a twin sets of deep arm swallowing love handle laze over their doorway jamming hips and inhumanly pillowy asses.";
			say "     Their legs have grown to the size of modest tree trunks as thick rings of doughy blubber have engulfed their plush cunts behind a curtain of toasty tallow, still though despite their size their legs nevertheless retain a certain shapely quality as stubborn of hardened muscle lay hidden beneath. Balanced atop their mammoth tums are mountainous M-cup breasts, decadently engorged with cream and maternal purpose, their groaning milk tanks cast the most adorable impression in the silky roof of the tender middles. While their areolas have blossomed into taur glisten sauce capped with tiny-by-comparison nips that gleam in the available light as rich beads of fatty cream dribble with their voluptuous curves. Your cow's arms too are graced with velvety folds perfect for cuddling your spawn as they take their first drinks. Watching over them and your lesser broodmares-to-be are the deep dwelling humans who have asserted their dominance over your human flock.";
			WaitLineBreak;
			say "     Another time you might have taken umbrage over this, yet their efficiency in keeping your egg machines fed and bred is a small price to pay for allowing them to manage your thralls. Besides, their contributions to the cause as they attend your spawn in lower level are in some ways worthy of praise, nor can you deny that their predatory maternal charms aren't pleasing in their own way. As the many days spent serving your young have endowed with lithe amazonian build and shapely DD's well suited for feeding your flight. Undeniably proud of their statue and conditions, they stride the purposeful strut that highly the toned athletic build and gentle yet restrained bounce of the assets. Their demeanor to has come to mimic yours as they take equal pride in status dragon breeders and enforcers of the cults purpose, true a part of you worries about their growing influence over your young, but the worshipful looks they cast in your direction and sheepishly blush simmering over their nimble bodies whenever you pause to inspect them stills such thoughts.";
		else if Loyalty of Dragon Cultist is 3;
			say "     Approaching the pinnacle of their ascension, your cults can barely even be considered human anymore as amidst the simmering cauldron of draconic heat coiling through the temple even the newest among their quickly begins to shed their feeble human. Meanwhile, you senior most members are gifted with large light capable wings and long prehensile spaded tails. Their busts continue to swell with glorious purpose as taut silky smooth milky mound could easily fill an G-cup bra, not that your cults would ever wish to cover up. For few things bring them greater glee then watching their scales slowly spreading along her toned athletic curves as their bodies are blanketed in velvety sheen of coldblooded perfection.  Overjoyed by this development and their shared love of their increasingly draconic bodies, your senior cultists are quick to find mates for their [']younger['] sisters and guide them through their first litters so that their peers may experience the ecstasy of flight of themselves.";
			say "     These blissful initiations have come to serve as a potent catalyst not just for change, but important bonding time for your loving followers as together they gush over their latest changes, or clutches with earnest delight. This has led to a huge population explosion as everywhere you look, your cultists are aglow with motherly purpose as their bellies and breasts ripen in preparation for their latest litter. Unrestrained by the petty notions of human decency, your dragons-to-do revel do all that they can to encourage their bodies and one another to embrace their true nature and divine purpose as mothers of your mighty flight. As each blessed inch gained or egg laid hastens Tiamat's arrival along with the salvation of this world under your draconic thumb. Soon, they often whisper to themselves and their slumbering young, their numbers will be large enough to spread this gift to masses, so all deserving souls may experience the eternal grace and majesty of draconic ascension, just as the five heads commands.";]

instead of conversing the Dragon Cultist:
	say "[dragonspeak]";

to say dragonspeak:
	if Morale of Arlene < 10:
		say "     Observing your Cultists scurrying about the halls on their way to and from their latest shifts, you doubt that your hard-working flock has much time to speak with you for any reasonable length of time. Much as it might please you to command their obedience, you think better of it as their hours are better toiling away on the temple ground than stroking your ego. Perhaps once your temple is better established and the ranks expanded, your followers can be afforded the luxury of conversing with your esteemed majesty. For now, you merely content yourself with listening to their idly chatter.";
		say "     [italic type]Author's note: more interactions between you and your flock will open up as your cult expands.[roman type]";
		LineBreak;
		let Filler_Choices be a list of text;
		add "Listen in?" to Filler_Choices;
		add "Ignore their prattle?" to Filler_Choices;
		let Filler_Choice be what the player chooses from Filler_Choices;
		if Filler_Choice is:
			-- "Listen in?":
				if Libido of Dragon Cultist is 0 and level of Dragon Cultist is 0:
					say "     Doing your best to appear aloof and disinterested, you turn to face a nearby lantern and make a show of inspecting it while your Cultists['] brief unfiltered chatter washes over you. [one of]'By the goddess, sister, I hope lady Arlene can get us some new mattresses! Even with the nanite's, my back is killing me,' one of the followers grumbles to her peers as she rubs the small of her back. 'I know, sister, but you have to admit it's still better than being stuck in the city,' the other cultist says in a soft comforting trill[or]'*Pst* hey, wanna head to the kitchen soon, I hear they're going to be passing out chocolate rations any minute now. If we hurry we'll get our pick of the litter,' a conspiratorial cultist whispers into one of her peer's ear. 'Really are you sure?' the other woman asks in a low voice while casting nervous looks to her fellows as they walk by. 'Ya, I have a friend working there and she put a few bars of dark chocolate aside for me, but we've got to hurry before the others start lining up,' her fellow titters, nodding towards the great hall. 'Alright let's make this quick, my shift's starting soon,' the other woman simpers as the two dart off[at random].";
					Increase level of Dragon Cultist by 1;
				else if Libido of Dragon Cultist is 0 and level of Dragon Cultist is 1:
					say "     Doing your best to appear aloof and disinterested, you turn to face a nearby lantern and make a show of inspecting it while your Cultists['] brief unfiltered chatter washes over you. 'Hey, have you been to the Chapel yet?' a rather awe-struck looking cultist asks as her and one of her sisters stroll down the hall. 'No, things have been so hectic I barely even have time to explore, and well,' the other woman pauses to a cast a quick glance to about the hall, 'don't tell mistress this, but I don't trust the Seradodovah there, they seem, I don't know... different,' her peer replies, sheepishly. 'I know what you mean, it's like they're looking though you, but seriously, you should really talk to Harbinger sometime. Shi is super sweet, and you wouldn't believe how yummy hir milk is,' her fellow says, idly licking her lips. 'Really?' the other woman inquires, raising a questioning eyebrow. 'Ya its like this wonderful mix of rich whole milk, energy drinks, and healing boosters,' her friend simpers. 'Ha, you're kidding right?' her peer chuckles.";
					say "     'Nopers,' the other woman titters, shaking her head, 'you should try some, a lot of us have been using it in place of coffee. Of course it's even better when you get it straight from the tap.' 'Y-you can't be serious?' her friend queries incredulously. 'Totally, you got to try some with me the next time we're on break. Trust me, it really helps with some of the longer shifts, and,' she pauses to lean in. 'If we promise to listen to one of hir lectures on the goddess we can skip our next shift.' 'Oh, but won't Lady Arlene be mad at us?' her friend asks, with a nervous look in her eyes as she glances about. 'No, the chapel is under Harbinger's control, so as long as we're there on 'business', shi can't do anything about it!' the enthusiastic woman crows, while making exaggerated air quotes. 'Nice, now I [bold type]have[roman type] to check this out,' her friend titter as the two scamper off towards the main hall.";
					Increase level of Dragon Cultist by 1;
				else if Libido of Dragon Cultist is 0 and level of Dragon Cultist is 2:
					say "     Doing your best to appear aloof and disinterested, you drift over to one of the unoccupied cells as you aimlessly look over the spartan amenities, while your Cultists['] brief unfiltered gossip unfolds in the background. [one of]'*sigh* Work, work, work, that's all we seem to do here,' one of your followers grumbles as her and another of your supplicants amble past. 'Well what were you expecting sister? The cult was just founded a while ago,' her fellow quips. 'I don't know, massive orgies, cool robes, maybe a secret handshake?' the woman snickers[or]'Say have you heard about the plans for the Moon Pool Lady Arlene and Harbinger have been discussing?' a cultist asks as she wanders by with a small group of fresh-faced supplicants. 'No, they've got me on kitchen duty, so I don't speak with members of the construction crews all that much,' a second cultist replies. 'Well I hear they're gonna to bring in some grow lights soon and maybe even put in some plants,' the first cultist says as they shuffle past. 'Really!? Oh that's wonderful! You would not believe how many times I've stubbed my toe walking around there,' a third supplicant exclaims[at random].";
					Increase level of Dragon Cultist by 1;
				else if Libido of Dragon Cultist is 0 and level of Dragon Cultist is 3:
					say "     Doing your best to appear aloof and disinterested, you drift over to one of the unoccupied cells as you aimlessly look over the spartan amenities, while your Cultists['] brief unfiltered gossip unfolds in the background. 'Hey, did you see the new recruits come in?' a cultist asks as she and one of her peers pause to chat outside the cell. 'No, I've been busy trying to learn this [']High Cant['] stuff to help manage the Seradovah these last few days, so everything's just been a total blur,' her fellow replies though a tired sigh. 'Well the poor dears were pretty banged up. According to them, some huskies have been kidnapping survivors. If it weren't for Mistress's flight they would have been caught too,' the first Cultist tuts as she shakes her head. 'Nothing new there sister, the ferals will grab just about anyone they can get their hands, er, paws on,' the other woman sighs. 'I know, but here's the thing, they-they weren't trying to turn them, from what I hear, those mean old pups are selling them somewhere,' the first supplicant says in a hushed whisper. 'Great, just what we need on top of everything else, slavers...' the second woman murmurs with a dejected shake of her head.";
					now level of Dragon Cultist is 0;
				else if Libido of Dragon Cultist >= 1 and level of Dragon Cultist is 0:
					say "     Muting your chromatophores, you idly paw into one of the darkened unoccupied cells, while a gaggle of your followers wander past you, seemingly unaware of your presence. 'Hey did you see what happened with you-know-who recently?' a grumpy-sounding cultist asks her peer as the two of them shuffle past the entrance to the vacant cell. 'Who?' her sister asks through a worn out huff. 'You know, [']her['],' the other replies, momentarily arching her back as she pats her stomach. 'Oh ya, [italic type]her[roman type], the lucky duck has been parading her stupid sexy tummy all over the place,' her peer rumbles, absently-mindedly pawing at her own vacant middle. 'I know and everyone is just fawning all over her any chance they get,' the grumpy cultist says as the two of them meander past. 'Ya its not that impressive, besides I bet you'd look even better with a cute little egg tummy,' her friend teases, cheekily pinching her sister's tight core. '*Tee-hee* thanks, but I know you'd rock that bump even harder, and you won't go rubbing that big cuddle tum in everyone's face like you-know-who,' the other woman giggles.";
					say "     'Ya though... I wouldn't mind it if you rubbed it in mine,' her peer swoons, as she tenderly brushes her fingers along the athletic curves of her adorable middle. 'Mh, I might hold you to that sister, I just hope they don't make me wait too long,' her friend purrs, tenderly cupping her now blushing tummy in her hands. 'I know how you feel, just think, one day we'll have a clutch of big sexy dergs all our own,' the other coos, pressing her lithe body against her peer. 'Ya just imagine getting to feel all those adorable widdle paws kicking?' the once grumpy cultist hums, wrapping her arms about her friend's waist as she draws her closer. 'Mh and maybe some nice big tits milky to boot,' her eager fellow preens as she affectionately presses shapely D's to her friends. 'Mh-mh, and we'll totally be super humble about it too, not like what's-her-face,' the now panting cultist murmurs. 'Ya, we won't brag about our little angels to anyone,' her friend titters, giving her peer's toned ass a loving squeeze. 'Or flaunt our cute shiny skin to passersby, unless they ask,' the lustful cultist replies as she leans in and kisses her way down the nape of her peer's neck.";
					WaitLineBreak;
					say "     'Or tease the others with our nice fat mommy milkers,' the other woman mews as her lewd companion nuzzles her face along the plush swell of her shapely sweater puppies. 'Or ask those big hunky nagas for foot rubs,' her peer teases, drawing her hand upwards along her fellow's svelte curves. 'Or play hooky all day with Harby or Lady Arlene,' the bawdy cultist rumbles, cupping her peer's cheeks in the palms of her hand. '*Ah* totally, we'll be the picture of a modest mommy, of course that doesn't mean we can't spoil each other, sister,' her fellow simpers, nodding towards a nearby cell with a deviant twinkle in her eyes. 'Oh naughty girl, you know our shift's going to start soon, but ah what the hell, come on,' her peer titters as she grabs her fellow's hand and leads her off to some of the more vacant sections of the cultist chambers.";
					Increase level of Dragon Cultist by 1;
				else if Libido of Dragon Cultist >= 1 and level of Dragon Cultist is 1:
					say "     Muting your chromatophores, you idly paw into one of the darkened unoccupied cells, while gaggles of your followers wander past you, seemingly unaware of your presence. 'Geeze, what does it take to get noticed around here? I keep heading down to the lower levels to see if any of those hunky snakes want to play, but I still haven't gotten any takers! Like, the fuck am I doing wrong!?' a pent up cultist whines as she strolls past with one of her snickering peers. 'Well you know they can't understand us right?' her chuckling fellow says. '*Pft* ya but you'd think they could take a hint at least!' the frustrated woman grumbles. 'Ha, I know, but maybe Harbinger can help you've seen the way they listen to hir and Lady Arlene,' the mirthful monkey hums, motioning towards The Chapel. 'Perhaps, but I'm not sure I wanna go in [']there['] cause well,' the pent up cultist pauses to glance to her left and right, 'I feel like there's something watching me.' 'Ya, I asked Harby about that once, shi says it's the goddess's eyes turning towards us,' her once tittering peer says reassuringly. 'Maybe, but why does it feel so strange like I'm being judged?' her fellow huffs.";
					say "     'Well, Harbinger says the goddess can feel our devotion to her so maybe...' the other woman whispers. 'I don't believe in her enough?' her peer rumbles, nervously rocking on the balls of her feet. 'I wouldn't say that, but perhaps you have just haven't opened yourself to her?' the once mirthful cultist proffers. 'But I-I have, its just...' the frustrated woman sighs. 'Scary?' her fellow asks in a neutral tone. 'Maybe, maybe coming here was a bad idea,' the flustered female grumbles. 'Now-now don't say that, sure this place is a little rough around the edges but it's getting better everyday. Besides, I think I know something that will help,' the other woman says in a kind matronly thrill. 'What?' the pensive woman replies. 'Well we can go see Harby together, and she can show you some of the goddess power and,' the kind human pauses to touch her hand to her tight middle, 'her love.'";
					WaitLineBreak;
					say "     'Really?' her peer asks, tilting her head at an inquisitive angle. 'Totally sister, even though the goddess's presence here is still weak, once you've carried a clutch of her favored servants, you'll see just how wondrous serving the five heads can be,' the mirthful maiden hums in a dreamy trill as she shamelessly massages her tight tum. 'Maybe, but I'm not sure I can lug around a big old eggy tummy on my shift,' the now curious woman purrs. 'Oh that's the best part. Harby will excuse you from your work while you're all nice egged up. Well,' the amorous pauses to tap her chin, 'at least once you start showing,' she adds, flashing her fellow a playful blep. '*Tee-hee* mh that does sound nice, but what's the catch?' the flustered female asks, raising a skeptical eye brow. 'Mh well their eggs do get pretty big,' the playful woman hums, dreamily rubbing her hands along the athletic contours of her tight core. 'How big?' her fellow says with a worried look in her eyes.";
					say "     'Ah dearest Tiamat, how I wish you could have seen me. Near the end of my first clutch I could barely get my arms around myself,' she swoons arching her back as she lazily traces her nails along the soft contours of her navel. 'Goddess, every inch of my tummy felt so ripe and sensitive, just the slightest breeze or touch was nearly enough to make me cum. Mh and my tits, oh blessed Tiamat I didn't even know the girls could get that big,' she says, drawing her arms impossibly wide as if to demonstrate her regal proportions. 'I swear you could hear the milk in them sloshing around with every breath, but it was all worth it,' the mirthful human pants. 'Why?' her fellow asks, in a hushed whisper. 'Because I could feel not just the goddess's love inside me, but her power filling me, changing me into the perfect vessel for her will... but only if I let it,' the mirthful woman pants as motes of many colors and none dance across her eyes. 'But what stopped you?' the pent up woman asks nervously.";
					WaitLineBreak;
					say "     'Because I'm not ready yet, no,' the mirthful human shakes her head, 'we're not ready sister to take the next step not while the great work on the temple remains unfinished. But,' she adds with a knowing smile, 'one day I think we'll be ready and then, I plan to finally let go, and begin again in the goddess arms.' 'So uh wa-what do you think will happen when you do?' the peer asks in a worried tone. 'I don't know but Harbinger says I'd might make a great queen if I'm earnest in my devotion, and freely give myself body, mind, and soul to the cause. Heavens, can you imagine that sister, me a queen?!' she cackles gesturing to her toned scaleless form with an odd look of disdain. 'Blessed Tiamat, I can scarcely dream of how wonderful it feel to be armored in her love,' she preens, gliding her nails just a hair too roughly across along her flanks. 'To eternally bask under the weight of her holy servants, to fill my womb with divine purpose,' she rambles as her hand drift back over blushing cunt.";
					say "     'Or minister to the lost peoples of this sphere and share with them the love of a god who will accept them for who they are, no matter how blessed or wretched they may be. However,' she continues, loosing a centering sigh, 'even if the goddess doesn't deem me worth, I want to serve Tiamat in whatever way I can, I want to fill the world with her chosen, and bring an end to all the horrible things happening on the mainland no matter the cost!' she roars, fixing her hands into the familiar two-head dragon symbol employed by her peers. Through all this, her pent up human looks on in a mix of confusion, awe, and fear. 'I-I-I,' she stammers, taking a step back before roughly bumping into the wall. 'I know sister its a lot to take in, but if just have a little faith, you'll see the glorious future Tiamat wishes to share with us, and even if you don't want to become like Harbinger, you can still share in the bliss, and time off, her servants can bestow,' she simpers sweetly as the fire fades from her voice. 'Mh oh what the heck, sure, I came this far already, and could use a day off,' the pent up human chuckles. 'That's the spirit sister, now come on lets go to The Chapel so Harby and I can introduce you to those hunky naga! Plus, we could really use the extra hands around here,' the jubilant human exclaims as grabs her peer by the hand and darts towards the main hall.";
					increase level of Dragon Cultist by 1;
				else if Libido of Dragon Cultist >= 1 and level of Dragon Cultist is 2:
					say "     Sashaying towards the entrance and the gloom-shrouded staircase leading down to your brood's private lair, you hastily mute your color-changing cells and watch as your followers filter about the area. Though little happens at first as your hard working supplicants trudge about the area on their way to and from their toils. All eyes are soon drawn to the lush glowing splendor of one of your gravid mates strutting through the area, even in the low light, her natural glow alongside her poised and confident stride seems to illuminate the halls as she parades her bountiful body about the chambers. Far traveled as you are, you're not fully immune to her charms, as though a part of you might have become used to seeing people in such lovely conditions, the sight of her ripening body brings a lustful smirk to your scalie lips as you watch the cute wobble of her plush milky breasts that accompanies her every step. Even from this distance, you just barely hear the subtle sloshing of her cream resounding through the halls as her fertile body prepares itself for your coming wyrmlings.";
					say "     Not that the gleeful human seems to mind, from the proud smirk on her face, she seems to revel in her growing mammary superiority. You can't help but wonder how big she'll get near the end either, as her flush mounds are already spilling over the prodigious curve of her gravid tumby. Laden with an untold number of eggs, her creamy skin is stretched delectably tight by the sheer weight of your titanic young, and you clearly see the beginning of deep rosy tiger stripes forming around her plush outie as her poor abused hide struggles to keep up with the accelerated growth of your brood that shows no signs of slowing down. As already her glistening middle neatly covers her plush cunt behind an adorable creamy sphere of fertile excess while her arm rests upon her hips as she strides through the halls. Seeming spellbound by her and your spawn's presence, your cultists quickly flock to her side, eager to lay hands on the slumbering forms of their saviors. 'Now-now little mouses, no pushing, there's plenty of tummy to go around,' your fecund follower hums as she directs her peers to make an orderly queue. Mewling plaintively, the others begrudgingly comply, shifting into a proper line before her, though some still try to push ahead.";
					WaitLineBreak;
					say "     A warning glance from your gravid plaything soon sorts them out, as she motions to the first supplicant to approach with a genial wave of her hand. Rumbling appreciatively, the star-struck cultist ambles forward and she kneels before your beaming plaything murmuring, 'Heavens sister you look radiant,' as she clasps her hands to her chest and flashes her peer the familiar two-head dragon symbol. 'Why, thank you dear, you have no idea how good this feels,' your lovely playmate preens, as she runs her hand over the hearty curves of her drum taut tum. 'It likes every fiber of my being is infused with the goddess's love. I've never felt so full before. Why, even now, I can sense them getting bigger and stronger by the second,' she rumbles in a near draconic trill. 'Really?' the worshipful woman asks. 'Mh, yes at times I can hear their thoughts, their pride, their power roiling in my chest as they dream within me. Goddess, I almost don't want this to end!' the doting breeder hums as she presses her voluptuous middle against her peer's face. 'Go on precious yor, have a listen, your lady's angels are eager to meet their supplicants,' she adds as the little human nods sheepishly, touching her ear to the other woman's puffy navel.";
					say "     'Goddess, y-yo-you're right, I can hear them!' the reverent cultist purrs, eyes going wide with delight at the light little quivering ripples simmering over her peer's overstretched tum. 'And that's just the echoes of their voices,' your plaything chuffs, gleefully groping a handful of her vast love handles. 'Imagine it sister; to hear such music reverberate through your being, to know you carry the seed of not just your salvation, but the world's within you,' she preens as she gazes at the wondrous swell of her opulent body. 'Blessed Tiamat, what I would give for this...' the fervent cultist hums, nuzzling her checks against her peer's glistening tummy. 'Don't worry sister, in time we'll all get to as well *Oof*,' the fecund cultist grunts, as a light series of kicks ripples across her core. '*Pant* oh *pant* my, I think the-the *gasp* little ones can feel your devotion to the cause, sister.' 'Zunni zul?' the spellbound bumpaholic asks, looking up at her with a deeply hopeful expression.";
					WaitLineBreak;
					say "     'Yes, they tell me that the fire in your belly will make a wondrous home for the goddess's avenging angels,' your domineering plaything hums as she gives her fellow a tender pat on the head. 'By the five heads I hope so, I've lost my friends, my family, my home, all of them gone in the blink of an eye!' the other woman croaks as she leans into her peer's touch. 'There-there sister, your goddess and her children will put everything right, and you might even see some of the fallen once more, but only if we serve,' the gravid human rumbles expectantly. 'As the five heads commands!' her fellow roars, wiping the tears from her eyes. 'Well spoken child,' your well-egged plaything says as motes of many colors and none briefly dance across her eyes. 'Now rise, in time you too will feel this bliss, and your future brood shall rain the holy vengeance upon ";
					if "Touched by Madness" is listed in feats of Player:
						say "the wicked, the mutant, and the heretic alike, ";
					else:
						say "her enemies, ";
					say "in due time,' your pregnant supplicant hisses in near ophidian trill as she tucks her nail under the other woman's chin and [']lifts['] her to her feet. 'Thank you sister,' the other woman simpers as she collects herself then ambles past her while the women behind look on in awe as the next in line bows before your mate's heaven bump. A similar scene repeats itself over and over as your gravid plaything fills their ears with honeyed words and doting praise while her peers heap their own worshipful wishes upon your slumbering spawn. Till at last, the halls are emptied and the now strangely tired and somewhat confused looking supplicant waddles off to her cell with a dreamy look in her eyes.";
					Increase level of Dragon Cultist by 1;
				else if Libido of Dragon Cultist >= 1 and level of Dragon Cultist is 3:
					say "     Sashaying towards the entrance of the gloom-shrouded staircase leading down to your brood's private lair, you hastily mute your color-changing cells and watch as your followers filter about the area. Though little happens at first as your hard working supplicants trudge about the area on their way to and from their toils. All eyes are soon drawn to the glowing splendor of one of your gravid mates strutting through the area. Despite in the low light, her natural glow alongside her poised and confident stride seems to illuminate the halls as she parades her bountiful body about the chambers. Even you are not fully immune to her charms, as though a part of you might have become used to seeing people in such lovely conditions, the sight of ripening body brings a lustful smirk to your scalie lips as you watch the cute wobble of her plush milky breasts that accompanies her every step. Lovely beads of pearly cream dribble from her plush pink ducts as her profoundly productive body does its best to provide for your slumbering titanic brood.";
					say "     Seemingly unbothered by the [']mess['], your gravid plaything appears profoundly proud of her leaky conditions as she idly massages her heavy mounds as they bounce delectably atop the sublime curves of her brood-swollen body. The thick rivulets of alabaster perfection seem to hug her deepening curves and plush flanks as the blissful changes creep across the once trim woman's athletic form. Beyond full and ripe with draconic life, her tummy easily obscures her fertile snatch behind a lustrous dome of precious maternal padding, befitting a brood mare of her growing stature. Cute rosy tiger stripes spiral around her puffy not-so-little turkey timer as her glowing porcelain-colored skin is stretched decadently tight by the weight of your spawn as the poor human's maternal body struggles to keep up with their impressive growth. Strangely, the gleeful mother-to-be doesn't seem encumbered in the slightest by her condition. If anything, her lush form almost radiates vitality as she proudly struts through the halls.";
					say "     All the while, her peers look on in a mix of jealousy and awe as the low hungry rumbles of your cultist's stomachs echo through the halls as they begin milling ever closer to your mate, bombarding her with questions about the condition of their saviours. Basking in their presence, your chosen graciously answers them with eager smiles and honeyed tales of her experience. 'Goddess, sisters, you wouldn't believe how wondrous this feels,' she hums, arching her back to better highlight her motherly glow and the velvety shimmer of her rotund tummy as the lantern lights twinkle across her too-tight skin. 'Its like my whole body is brimming with energy and purpose,' she rumbles in near draconic cadence as she drapes her arms worshipfully over the ponderous swell of her eggy middle. 'Really?' an inquisitive supplicant asks, tilting her head to one side. 'Yes sister, thanks to the little ones here,' she titters, lightly drumming her finger along her deepening hem line.";
					WaitLineBreak;
